armys read this!!!


As yall might know BTS is going to release their album on 21st feb and the title track will be uploaded in YT.
So here’s the thing. BTS has got a lot of attention from non kpop stans and locals through Black Swan. By trending in twitter and through scammy BTS has got a lot of attention than before. Pretty sure a lot of non stans are going to check them out this comeback.

Keep the comments clean. Don’t spam unnecessarily. IK it’s beautiful to see fans worldwide (mostly Latin) chanting the same thing “BTS is the best” “Love from xxx”
But such comments are hiding other valuable comments that talk on real things - about the song!

Let’s comment about the mvs aesthetics, the lyrics and theories instead of spamming. That’d be beautiful.


And for god’s sake please don’t comment “wHo LoVes BTS? 👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻”
Comment something worth the likes. And let’s make a welcoming atmosphere for be fans 💜
